room_title: Escape room "No Ship Sherlock" by Escape SBC in Shreveport
room_description: Sherlock Holmes’ prized Ship In A Bottle has gone missing!  He and Dr. Watson are too busy with other cases to be able to investigate what happened to it. So, Sherlock has hired your team of detective interns to investigate and find his beloved ship.  Can you impress Sherlock Holmes and Dr. Watson by finding the missing ship and possibly earn a job as one of Sherlock’s new assistants?  221B Baker Street awaits you!
